comments: Simons (POR) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Caruso (CHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Simons (POR).
DeRozan (CHI) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
DeRozan (CHI) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from Simons (POR) during the driving shot attempt.
Vucevic's (CHI) left forearm makes contact with the ball as he defends Simons' (POR) shot near the rim.
Banton (POR) and Bitim (CHI) briefly engage and disengage off ball.

Bitim (CHI) moves laterally into Banton's (POR) path and initiates contact with Banton's arm that causes him to lose possession.  The contact occurs after Banton's gather on a drive that could end inside the LDB, and a shooting foul was warranted.
Simons (POR) swipes down and initiates contact to Caruso's (CHI) arm which affects his driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) contests Simons' (POR) jump shot, and the marginal contact occurs as Simons brings his leg forward towards Caruso.
Walker (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Vucevic (CHI).
Reath (POR) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Bulls.
Vucevic (CHI) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the ball is deflected away by Walker (POR).  Upon regaining possession, Vucevic turns to shoot within three seconds.
Walker (POR) moves alongside Vucevic's (CHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the post shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
Banton (POR) commits a take foul on DeRozan (CHI).
Caruso (CHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Simons (POR) as he is starting his upward shooting motion.
Caruso (CHI) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Trail Blazers.
